🧩 Tech Stack & Architectuur

Frontend: React + TypeScript + Vite + TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui + lucide-react.

Backend: Netlify Functions (TypeScript/Node). Nova-function gebruikt OpenAI (env: OPENAI_API_KEY).

Data: Supabase (auth, lichte tabellen zoals user_gamification).

Routing: code-splitting (lazy imports), error boundaries + health route (/__health).

Analytics: event helper w(...) (b.v. nova_message_send, nova_response_generated).

Build & performance: lazy/lite, geen zware assets inline, responsive images, prefetch waar zinvol.

